#: src/fsearch_cli_config.c:111
msgid ""
"Usage: fsearch config COMMAND [OPTIONS]\n"
"\n"
"View and modify the shared FSearch GUI and CLI configuration.\n"
"\n"
"Configuration commands:\n"
"  path                         Print the configuration file path\n"
"  show [SECTION] [--json]      Show settings\n"
"  get KEY [--json]             Print one scalar setting\n"
"  set KEY VALUE                Set one scalar setting\n"
"  unset KEY                    Restore one scalar setting default\n"
"  reset [KEY|SECTION] --yes [--rescan]\n"
"                               Restore defaults\n"
"  doctor                       Check configuration and index consistency\n"
"  roots list|add|set|remove    Manage indexed roots\n"
"  excludes list|add|remove|hidden\n"
"                               Manage index exclusions\n"
"  filters list|add|set|remove|reset\n"
"                               Manage saved search filters\n"
"\n"
"Scalar values use true/false, decimal integers, or strings.\n"
"Run 'fsearch config show' to list every scalar key and current value.\n"
"Scalar sections: search, application, window, ui, columns, sort, dialogs.\n"
"Use 'fsearch config roots|excludes|filters --help' for family options.\n"
"Close the FSearch GUI before changing shared settings.\n"
"Index changes become searchable on the next CLI search, or immediately with "
"--rescan.\n"
"Use --json with show, get, and collection list commands.\n"
"\n"
"Examples:\n"
"  fsearch config show search --json\n"
"  fsearch config get search.match-case\n"
"  fsearch config set search.match-case true\n"
"  fsearch config roots add ~/Code --monitor --one-file-system --rescan\n"
"  fsearch config excludes add '*.tmp' --type wildcard --scope basename --"
"target files\n"
"  fsearch config filters add Documents --query 'ext:pdf' --macro docs\n"
"  fsearch config reset search --yes\n"
msgstr ""
"Paggamit: fsearch config COMMAND [OPTIONS]\n"
"\n"
"Tingnan at baguhin ang nakabahaging FSearch GUI at CLI configuration.\n"
"\n"
"Mga utos sa pagsasaayos:\n"
"  path                         I-print ang path ng configuration file\n"
"  show [SECTION] [--json]      Ipakita ang mga setting\n"
"  get KEY [--json]             Mag-print ng isang setting ng scalar\n"
"  set KEY VALUE                Magtakda ng isang setting ng scalar\n"
"  unset KEY                    Ibalik ang isang default na setting ng scalar\n"
"  reset [KEY|SECTION] --yes [--rescan]\n"
"                               Ibalik ang mga default\n"
"  doctor                       Suriin ang configuration at pagkakapare-pareho ng index\n"
"  roots list|add|set|remove    Pamahalaan ang mga na-index na ugat\n"
"  excludes list|add|remove|hidden\n"
"                               Pamahalaan ang mga pagbubukod ng index\n"
"  filters list|add|set|remove|reset\n"
"                               Pamahalaan ang mga naka-save na filter sa paghahanap\n"
"\n"
"Gumagamit ang mga scalar value ng true/false, decimal integer, o string.\n"
"Patakbuhin ang 'fsearch config show' upang ilista ang bawat scalar key at kasalukuyang halaga.\n"
"Mga seksyon ng scaler: search, application, window, ui, columns, sort, dialogs.\n"
"Gumamit ng 'fsearch config roots|excludes|filter --help' para sa mga opsyon sa pamilya.\n"
"Isara ang FSearch GUI bago baguhin ang mga nakabahaging setting.\n"
"Ang mga pagbabago sa index ay nagiging mahahanap sa susunod na paghahanap sa CLI, o kaagad sa --rescan.\n"
"Gumamit ng --json na may mga command na show, get, at collection list.\n"
"\n"
"Mga halimbawa:\n"
"  fsearch config show search --json\n"
"  fsearch config get search.match-case\n"
"  fsearch config set search.match-case true\n"
"  fsearch config roots add ~/Code --monitor --one-file-system --rescan\n"
"  fsearch config excludes add '*.tmp' --type wildcard --scope basename --target files\n"
"  fsearch config filters add Documents --query 'ext:pdf' --macro docs\n"
"  fsearch config reset search --yes\n"

#: src/fsearch_cli_config.c:152
msgid ""
"Usage: fsearch config show [SECTION] [--json]\n"
"Show all scalar settings or one dotted section.\n"
msgstr ""
"Paggamit: fsearch config show [SECTION] [--json]\n"
"Ipakita ang lahat ng setting ng scalar o isang tuldok na seksyon.\n"

#: src/fsearch_cli_config.c:154
msgid ""
"Usage: fsearch config get KEY [--json]\n"
"Print one typed scalar value. Discover keys with 'fsearch config show'.\n"
msgstr ""
"Paggamit: fsearch config get KEY [--json]\n"
"Mag-print ng isang nai-type na scalar value. Tuklasin ang mga key na may 'fsearch config show'.\n"

#: src/fsearch_cli_config.c:157
msgid ""
"Usage: fsearch config set KEY VALUE\n"
"Set a boolean, integer, string, or enumerated scalar value.\n"
msgstr ""
"Paggamit: fsearch config set KEY VALUE\n"
"Magtakda ng boolean, integer, string, o enumerated scalar value.\n"

#: src/fsearch_cli_config.c:159
msgid ""
"Usage: fsearch config unset KEY\n"
"Restore one scalar setting to its built-in default.\n"
msgstr ""
"Paggamit: fsearch config unset KEY\n"
"Ibalik ang isang setting ng scalar sa built-in na default nito.\n"

#: src/fsearch_cli_config.c:161
msgid ""
"Usage: fsearch config reset [KEY|SECTION] --yes [--rescan]\n"
"Reset is destructive and requires --yes. --rescan applies to roots, "
"database, excludes, or all.\n"
msgstr ""
"Paggamit: fsearch config reset [KEY|SECTION] --yes [--rescan]\n"
"Ang pag-reset ay nakakasira at nangangailangan ng --oo. --rescan ay nalalapat sa mga ugat, database, hindi kasama, o lahat.\n"

#: src/fsearch_cli_config.c:164
msgid ""
"Usage: fsearch config doctor\n"
"Check configuration readability and whether the saved index uses the same "
"roots and exclusions.\n"
msgstr ""
"Paggamit: fsearch config doctor\n"
"Suriin ang pagiging madaling mabasa ng configuration at kung ang naka-save na index ay gumagamit ng parehong mga ugat at pagbubukod.\n"

#: src/fsearch_cli_config.c:170
msgid ""
"Usage: fsearch config roots COMMAND [PATH] [OPTIONS]\n"
"\n"
"Commands:\n"
"  list [--json]                List indexed roots\n"
"  add PATH [OPTIONS]           Add a root directory\n"
"  set PATH [OPTIONS]           Change an existing root\n"
"  remove PATH [--rescan]       Remove an existing root\n"
"\n"
"Options for add and set:\n"
"  --active, --inactive\n"
"  --monitor, --no-monitor\n"
"  --one-file-system, --no-one-file-system\n"
"  --scan-after-launch, --no-scan-after-launch\n"
"  --rescan-every SECONDS        Set periodic rescan interval; 0 disables it\n"
"  --rescan                      Rebuild the index immediately after saving\n"
msgstr ""
"Paggamit: fsearch config roots COMMAND [PATH] [OPTIONS]\n"
"\n"
"Mga utos:\n"
"  list [--json]                Ilista ang mga na-index na ugat\n"
"  add PATH [OPTIONS]           Magdagdag ng root directory\n"
"  set PATH [OPTIONS]           Baguhin ang isang umiiral na ugat\n"
"  remove PATH [--rescan]       Alisin ang isang umiiral na ugat\n"
"\n"
"Mga opsyon para sa pagdaragdag at pag-set:\n"
"  --active, --inactive\n"
"  --monitor, --no-monitor\n"
"  --one-file-system, --no-one-file-system\n"
"  --scan-after-launch, --no-scan-after-launch\n"
"  --rescan-every SECONDS        Magtakda ng pana-panahong agwat ng muling pag-scan; 0 ay hindi pinagana ito\n"
"  --rescan                      Buuin muli ang index kaagad pagkatapos i-save\n"

#: src/fsearch_cli_config.c:187
msgid ""
"Usage: fsearch config excludes COMMAND [PATTERN|VALUE] [OPTIONS]\n"
"\n"
"Commands:\n"
"  list [--json]                 List exclusions\n"
"  add PATTERN [OPTIONS]         Add an exclusion\n"
"  remove PATTERN [OPTIONS]      Remove a matching exclusion\n"
"  hidden [true|false] [--rescan]\n"
"                                View or change hidden-file exclusion\n"
"\n"
"Options for add and remove:\n"
"  --type fixed|wildcard|regex   Default: fixed\n"
"  --scope full-path|basename    Default: full-path\n"
"  --target both|files|folders   Default: both\n"
"  --active, --inactive          Add state or removal selector\n"
"  --rescan                      Rebuild the index immediately after saving\n"
msgstr ""
"Paggamit: fsearch config excludes COMMAND [PATTERN|VALUE] [OPTIONS]\n"
"\n"
"Mga utos:\n"
"  list [--json]                 Maglista ng mga pagbubukod\n"
"  add PATTERN [OPTIONS]         Magdagdag ng pagbubukod\n"
"  remove PATTERN [OPTIONS]      Mag-alis ng katugmang pagbubukod\n"
"  hidden [true|false] [--rescan]\n"
"                                Tingnan o baguhin ang nakatagong pagbubukod ng file\n"
"\n"
"Mga opsyon para sa pagdaragdag at pag-alis:\n"
"  --type fixed|wildcard|regex   Default: naayos\n"
"  --scope full-path|basename    Default: full-path\n"
"  --target both|files|folders   Default: pareho\n"
"  --active, --inactive          Magdagdag ng tagapili ng estado o pag-alis\n"
"  --rescan                      Buuin muli ang index kaagad pagkatapos i-save\n"

#: src/fsearch_cli_config.c:204
msgid ""
"Usage: fsearch config filters COMMAND [NAME] [OPTIONS]\n"
"\n"
"Commands:\n"
"  list [--json]                 List saved filters\n"
"  add NAME [OPTIONS]            Add a named filter\n"
"  set NAME [OPTIONS]            Change a named filter\n"
"  remove NAME                   Remove a named filter\n"
"  reset                         Restore built-in filters\n"
"\n"
"Options for add and set:\n"
"  --query QUERY                 Saved FSearch query\n"
"  --macro MACRO                 Query macro name\n"
"  --case, --no-case             Match case\n"
"  --path, --no-path             Search full paths\n"
"  --regex, --no-regex           Treat query as a regular expression\n"
msgstr ""
"Paggamit: fsearch config filters COMMAND [NAME] [OPTIONS]\n"
"\n"
"Mga utos:\n"
"  list [--json]                 Ilista ang mga naka-save na filter\n"
"  add NAME [OPTIONS]            Magdagdag ng pinangalanang filter\n"
"  set NAME [OPTIONS]            Baguhin ang isang pinangalanang filter\n"
"  remove NAME                   Alisin ang isang pinangalanang filter\n"
"  reset                         Ibalik ang mga built-in na filter\n"
"\n"
"Mga opsyon para sa pagdaragdag at pag-set:\n"
"  --query QUERY                 Naka-save na query sa FSearch\n"
"  --macro MACRO                 Query macro name\n"
"  --case, --no-case             Kaso ng tugma\n"
"  --path, --no-path             Maghanap ng buong mga landas\n"
"  --regex, --no-regex           Tratuhin ang query bilang isang regular na expression\n"

